inlineContent.text: Internet password keychain items are usually used to save passwords for network services. They are stored as UTF-8 encoded strings in the keychain.

Due to an issue / limitation in iOS 12, the synchronous query methods are only available for iOS 13 and later.
With iOS 12 a synchronous query on the main thread leads to a deadlock when the keychain services try to display a UI due to an access control restriction.
